title: Quintin Esterhuizen
text:
Quintin Esterhuizen (born ) is a Namibian <a href="rugby%20union">rugby union</a> player, currently playing with the <a href="Namibia%20national%20rugby%20union%20team">Namibia national team</a>. His regular position is prop.
Rugby career.
Esterhuizen was born in <a href="Springs%2C%20Gauteng">Springs</a> in <a href="South%20Africa">South Africa</a>, but grew up in <a href="Windhoek">Windhoek</a>. He was selected to represent Namibia at Under-16 and Under-18 level between 2010 and 2012, and made his test debut for in 2014 against . He also represented the in the South African domestic <a href="Currie%20Cup">Currie Cup</a> and <a href="Vodacom%20Cup">Vodacom Cup</a> competitions since 2015.
